Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被稱作月神2號的第2月球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.48,0:01:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是被用於建設宇宙都市使用的\N擁有大量礦物資源的小行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.57,0:01:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它旁邊的第七號宇宙都市SIDE 7開始建造的第二年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍的戰爭開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.82,0:01:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於這場大戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四個宇宙都市群消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.84,0:02:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下SIDE 6中僅有的幾個宇宙都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.61,0:02:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而ZION公國所在的宇宙都市群卻在離地球最遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.86,0:02:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的總帥基連·薩比叫囂著要討伐軟弱的地球聯邦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.18,0:02:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能拯救人類命運的只有他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『庫克魯斯·德安之島』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.98,0:02:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機 阿姆羅 ，聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運輸機出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，開始連接時我會倒數的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.76,0:02:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是縮短3秒，明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，開始準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切OK！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，連接程序妥當了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，請你將連接畫面對準！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已將畫面對準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5、4、3、2、1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.62,0:03:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投下B零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換位置，連接開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部用了19秒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以縮短4秒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為激光畫面照準很慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.75,0:03:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，剛接到空軍的緊急訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是求救嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地點和敵軍數目呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.96,0:04:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是用自動訊號機發出的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不能通訊，馬上計算出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐標305
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.76,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地點是305，很接近！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫阿姆羅去偵察吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫阿姆羅把核戰機和GUNDAM分體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.81,0:04:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用核戰機去巡邏305！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.11,0:04:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，我要解體了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.88,0:04:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請接收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 真不想看這場面呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，我出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不想這看見GUNDAM像頭小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地點是305...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這島了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還生存？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.55,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，盡量問清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，有什麼需馬上送過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎聯邦軍也不會救自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定附近有埋伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫大家準備應戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.33,0:05:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.58,0:06:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不成了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.75,0:06:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要亂動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.65,0:06:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪\N只將他們生檎綁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,及拿走了武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些軍人別過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.81,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣！停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是敵人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走！不要來這小島！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你們停手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起去弄壞戰鬥機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這次不好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！德安回來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.91,0:07:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方應該不是ZION軍的領地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有軍人來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還用鎗指著我們呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒意思交戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將武器交出，不會傷害你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交武器給你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈非任你魚肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是不想作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才要你交出武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們先去安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安，你要打贏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單靠戰機就可以對付我了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能毀滅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只要打中要害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.70,0:08:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都可以令你動不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.04,0:08:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要破壞你關節部份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很敏捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫羅娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是德安和孩子之家！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.57,0:10:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庫克魯斯·德安 是他救你回來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安准你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.24,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你養好傷前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏休息一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.71,0:10:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑！我的戰機在那？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說得沒錯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在菜園的後面和孩子們一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安，他來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以起來行動了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.38,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底收在那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.59,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說那戰機？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.22,0:11:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要保護這些孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知ZION遲早會發現這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會來攻擊我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要有武器保護才成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你把核戰機還給我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還給你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.34,0:11:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會來攻擊我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不似你要小孩當手下那樣卑鄙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要對付ZION的侵略者！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你說德安壞話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒騙我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！保護小島是錯的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.85,0:11:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說他壞\N請走吧！走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然騙得他們入迷了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.53,0:11:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些無謂的爭執別斤斤計較！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會尋回核戰機的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他一定搬不遠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安，他會找到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會給他找到吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.02,0:12:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你似乎比我想像中固執呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是來監視我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看，你連夕陽有多美也不知呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭時根本就不需知美不美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一放鬆便會敗下來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安並非人想像中的壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他騙孩子的技術很了得呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那德安...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不知真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別亂說好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要收起我的核戰機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是...為什麼還不瞭解！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.59,0:14:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為他們年紀小就易受騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他來到這小島嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，德安為何要照顧他們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你想知，就自己去問吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知德安很稱讚你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說只要洗脫幼氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是個好軍人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他似乎不在這小島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.89,0:14:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良！明天搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回母艦吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再多一會吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在每個人也很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該和我們聯絡的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有他原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.78,0:14:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣最好，但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為何要胡思亂想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有ZION軍蹤影...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還未睡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想怎樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指那年青人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看是困不著他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能他的同伴也在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不改變他的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.90,0:15:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每日也要提心吊膽的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的話我也想離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到他了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.70,0:16:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.37,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別拋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎大家都沒睡好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我繼續去找吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.05,0:16:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有物體接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.55,0:16:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且速度很快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向這邊來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.55,0:16:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！是305方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派良去好嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！母艦也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.72,0:16:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.90,0:17:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快些走！走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快離開這島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是ZAKU？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？那些小孩呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.87,0:17:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.87,0:17:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.60,0:17:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安！快還我那核戰機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.72,0:17:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安...跟我來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那機動戰士在攻擊什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅？沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.76,0:18:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲些再說吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右面的機動戰士是幫助我們的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！你還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.44,0:18:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你立即發射GUNDAM出來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要在空中結合！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.87,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先回母艦吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倉庫準備幫他換裝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我技術已進步了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只餘這ZAKU了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！這個由我來處理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你沒有武器啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你看看機動戰士的博鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好在一邊看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...德安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別來！但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.57,0:19:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要那班小孩仍看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.74,0:19:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安，打敗他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打低這機械人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不明白！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想知嗎？少年們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死這班小孩父母的兇手就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我射擊的流彈打中他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION軍要我連小孩也殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...我難以下手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我帶走了他們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我也死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦絕不讓人傷害這班小孩子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.19,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕不可讓人傷害...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些孩子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安，你真勇敢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是我們首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想只要我一日在世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也絕不放過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有我在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而他們亦不會安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...不知怎辦好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.87,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你錯了！那不是因為你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為你體內那種濃烈的戰鬥氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.18,0:21:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這種殺氣吸引他們來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥氣味？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我幫你消滅它吧！庫克魯斯·德安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.08,0:22:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼？太過份了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不應這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.80,0:22:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德安！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.90,0:22:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真該死！可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.40,0:22:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手，別這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.80,0:22:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們別生哥哥氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.40,0:22:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他拋你的機械人到海裏呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.07,0:22:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他所做的事是非常之對的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.41,0:22:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅娜，這年青人真的不錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.58,0:22:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.59,0:22:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現在沙漠中的蓋洛普和古夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.91,0:23:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要知道夏亞消息的雪拉違反命令而出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.62,0:23:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她無謀的戰鬥使GUNDAM陷入危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅的救援作戰是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.17,0:23:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.86,0:23:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『雪拉出擊』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.51,0:23:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

